# Troubleshooting Guide

## Common Issues and Solutions

### Build Issues

#### TypeScript Compilation Errors
- **Issue**: TypeScript errors during build
- **Solution**:
  - Check [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) configuration
  - Run `npm run lint:fix` to auto-fix issues
  - Ensure all imports are properly typed

#### Vite Build Failures
- **Issue**: Vite build fails
- **Solution**:
  - Check [vite.config.ts](mdc:vite.config.ts) configuration
  - Verify path aliases are correct (`@` maps to `/src`)
  - Ensure all dependencies are installed

### Development Issues

#### Hot Reload Not Working
- **Issue**: Changes not reflecting in browser
- **Solution**:
  - Restart dev server with `npm run dev`
  - Check for syntax errors in console
  - Clear browser cache

#### Import Path Issues
- **Issue**: Module not found errors
- **Solution**:
  - Use `@/` prefix for src imports (e.g., `@/components/landing/FeaturesSection`)
  - Check file extensions (.tsx for components)
  - Verify file exists in correct location

### Component Issues

#### React.FC vs Function Components
- **Issue**: Inconsistency in component definitions
- **Solution**:
  - **ALWAYS** use function declarations: `export function Component() {}`
  - **NEVER** use `React.FC`: `export const Component: React.FC = () => {}`
  - This is a project-wide standard for consistency

#### Button Component Problems
- **Issue**: Button styling not working
- **Solution**:
  - Check [src/components/design-system/button/Button.tsx](mdc:src/components/design-system/button/Button.tsx) for correct variant usage
  - Ensure proper className merging with `cn()` utility
  - Verify Tailwind classes are valid

#### Navigation Issues
- **Issue**: Navigation not working
- **Solution**:
  - Check [src/components/TopNavigation.tsx](mdc:src/components/TopNavigation.tsx) for anchor link configuration
  - Verify routes in [src/App.tsx](mdc:src/App.tsx) match navigation links
  - Ensure React Router is properly configured
  - For anchor links, verify section IDs match (features, how-it-works, faq)

#### Anchor Link Scrolling
- **Issue**: Clicking nav links doesn't scroll to section
- **Solution**:
  - Ensure section has correct `id` attribute (e.g., `id="features"`)
  - Check `scrollToSection` function in TopNavigation
  - Verify smooth scrolling behavior is supported

### Styling Issues

#### Tailwind Classes Not Working
- **Issue**: Tailwind classes not applying
- **Solution**:
  - Check if Tailwind is properly configured
  - Verify class names are correct
  - Use `cn()` utility for conditional classes
  - Check for CSS conflicts

#### Dark Theme Issues
- **Issue**: Components don't respect dark theme
- **Solution**:
  - Use zinc-950 for backgrounds, zinc-100 for text
  - Use violet-500/10 for accent backgrounds
  - Check [src/index.css](mdc:src/index.css) for ViralClips brand colors

#### Responsive Design Issues
- **Issue**: Mobile/desktop styles not working
- **Solution**:
  - Use mobile-first approach with Tailwind breakpoints
  - Test with [src/hooks/use-mobile.tsx](mdc:src/hooks/use-mobile.tsx) hook
  - Check browser dev tools for responsive behavior

### Landing Page Issues

#### Logo Not Displaying
- **Issue**: ViralClips logo not showing
- **Solution**:
  - Check logo imports in TopNavigation and Footer
  - Verify [src/assets/viralclips-logo.svg](mdc:src/assets/viralclips-logo.svg) exists
  - Check dark/light variant usage based on page background

#### Platform Carousel Not Animating
- **Issue**: Logo carousel not moving
- **Solution**:
  - Check CSS animation in [src/index.css](mdc:src/index.css) (scroll-left keyframes)
  - Verify LogosCarousel component props
  - Check for CSS conflicts with animation

### Legal Pages Issues

#### Terms/Privacy Page Not Found
- **Issue**: /terms or /privacy routes not working
- **Solution**:
  - Verify routes in [src/App.tsx](mdc:src/App.tsx)
  - Check [src/pages/Terms.tsx](mdc:src/pages/Terms.tsx) and [src/pages/Privacy.tsx](mdc:src/pages/Privacy.tsx) exist
  - Ensure Footer links use correct paths

### Performance Issues

#### Slow Build Times
- **Issue**: Build takes too long
- **Solution**:
  - Check for unnecessary dependencies
  - Optimize imports (use specific imports)
  - Consider code splitting for large components

#### Bundle Size Issues
- **Issue**: Large bundle size
- **Solution**:
  - Use dynamic imports for route-based code splitting
  - Optimize images and assets
  - Remove unused dependencies

### Linting Issues

#### Biome Errors
- **Issue**: Biome linting errors
- **Solution**:
  - Run `npm run lint:fix` to auto-fix
  - Check [biome.json](mdc:biome.json) configuration
  - Review error messages for specific issues

## Debugging Tips

### Console Debugging
- Use browser dev tools for component inspection
- Check React DevTools for component state
- Monitor network requests for API issues

### TypeScript Debugging
- Use strict TypeScript mode
- Check type definitions for components
- Use proper interface definitions

